headline: Agilent Introduces the Altura Line of Inert HPLC Columns for Superior Results in Biotherapeutic Testing
summary: SANTA CLARA, Calif., September 29, 2025--Agilent Technologies Inc. (NYSE: A) today announced the release of a new range of high performance liquid chromatography (HPLC) columns ideally suited for biotherapeutics applications. The Agilent Altura Ultra Inert HPLC Columns set a new standard in liquid chromatography performance, providing the reliability and efficiency biopharmaceutical companies need for the most demanding applications, including peptide GLP-1 and oligonucleotide therapeutic develo

headline: 1 Cash-Producing Stock with Impressive Fundamentals and 2 We Question
summary: While strong cash flow is a key indicator of stability, it doesn’t always translate to superior returns. Some cash-heavy businesses struggle with inefficient spending, slowing demand, or weak competitive positioning.
